                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 172.) I took Price in a pub<lb></lb>lic-house in Old-street—I said it was for tools, and he had better say what he had to say to the Magistrate—he said M'Donald had some tools, and they sold them and parted the money.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>) (Price received a good character.)</p>
